author: msmash
title: Texas Plans To Sue Google for Alleged Anticompetitive Behavior
description: Texas Attorney General Ken Paxton announced Wednesday that he will soon file a multistate antitrust lawsuit against Google and its advertising business, alleging that the company has stifled competition and enjoys "monopolistic power." From a report: In a twe…
